quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  2,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  2,2,"Ndeen deftere sikke alaa he mayre, ko nde peewal wonande hul…ìe …ìe"
  2,3,∆Åeen goon…óinoo…ìe mbirniindi e…ìe √±ii…ìna juulde e…ìe nafga e ko Min nje…ói …ìe
  2,4,"E …ìeen goon…óinoo…ìe ko Min njippini dow maa e ko jippinaa ado ma, e…ìe njananaa √±alaande wattan"
  2,5,"∆Åeen dey ngoni ko e peewal iwngal e Joomii …ìe, ko kam…ìe ngoni da…óoo…ìe"
